### Input Data

The analyses in this repository are based on publicly available scRNA-seq datasets deposited in the Gene Expression Omnibus (GEO):

* GSE325995 (Unmanipulated scRNA-seq)
* GSE327449 (CellTag scRNA-seq Experiment 1)
* GSE326529 (CellTag and Hashtag scRNA-seq Experiment 2)

